social_posts.post_text: On this rainy NYC day, we decided to check out the men’s and women’s basketball doubleheader at @columbia. #roarlionroar #family #nyc #basketball #rainyday #hoodieseason
Good morning. There’s never a dull moment with the Holdsclaw crew. Cairo laid out a full itinerary before 10am 🤦🏾‍♀️ #family #love #siblings #goodmorning #toddler #babygirl #weekend

Happy 3rd birthday, son. It’s such an honor to be your mom. I’m so grateful to watch you grow into a confident, intelligent, and compassionate individual. Every morning before you leave home, hearing you say, “ I will not hit my friends; I will be kind,” reminds me that I’m doing something right 🤣. I can’t wait to ride with you 🚴‍♀️ #happybirthday #sonshine #toddler #toddlerlife #family #woombikes
My homie @qmorrow1908 pulled up for the day in NYC. We had to hit Harlem and BK. Glad she got to chill with my family. Love you sis. #friendship #hoopers #nyc #sisterhood.
Just hanging with the family in these BK streets. #family #brooklyn #hoopers #blessed #nyc  #livinglife #sisterhood #family

I can’t believe our little Camdyn Rose turned one today. She was born on our Anniversary and today also makes six years of marriage. I’m so grateful for my life and tired. 🤣 #babygirl #family #happybirthday #instagood #daughter #anniversary
Wishing you all a wonderful holiday season filled with peace and love. #family #happyholidays #blessed #gratitude #lovewins #joy #love #peace
I had such a fun time today hanging out with my girls. The simple things bring me so much joy ❤️ #family #joy #lovewins #friday #newjersey #girlsday

This morning we went to our sons' first basketball practice. He just turned three and has asked me to take him to the park to play basketball. When I told him he could practice with uncle Matty @m_lp12 one day, he didn’t forget and asked every day. 🤣. When we got back to the car after practice, he said to me, “ We need to practice dribbling” 🤣🤣🤣. I got you son ❤️ #toddlerlife #toddler #basketball #family #momlife #sports #sundayvibes #parenthood #luckylefty

social_posts.post_text: Our big boy was finally ready for his first trim. Thank you to Kara at @pigtailsmontclair for making his first haircut/ trim a wonderful experience. This place is so awesome for the little ones. #firsthaircut #toddler #toddlerlife #boymom #sonshine #toddlermom #pigtailsandcrewcuts

Last week I met up in Knoxville, Tn, with one of my favorite college teammates, Abby Conklin @a52signs. It was so good to support Kellie and @ladyvol_hoops. I appreciated all the love and the familiar faces who have supported our program throughout the years. It was also great to catch up with my hoop sis @staley05, whom I just love ❤️. I can’t forget the laughs @buck1422 blesses me with every time we link. It’s was less than 24 hrs, but it was definitely what I needed 🫶🏾. #ladyvols #knoxville #sisterhood #rockytop #lvfl #vfl #volnation #universityoftennessee 🧡🧡🍊🍊

Last week the @celtics hosted me. It was a great time connecting with their community. I enjoyed catching up with my hoop sisters @allison_feaster & @ashleybattle. 

Thanks, @thesportzdoc for choosing me to join you in the conversation around mental health. 

The trip was filled with great vibrations. I found out Tony (@beyoutiful03) gives out amazing hugs. ❤️. I discovered @ellamai has a beautiful voice. I’m so glad I went to the concert. I had the chance to catch up with fellow UT alum @grantwill2 🧡🍑 and met one of my favorite athletes @jaytatum0 🫶🏾 #bostonceltics #boston #mentalhealth #mentalhealthawareness #nba
Grateful. Happy Mother’s Day #family #familytime #mothersday #twomoms #loveislove

Fun times last night celebrating with my H.S. teammates. We are getting old 🤦🏾‍♀️.⁣
⁣
Happy birthday @erinfahy 🎉. It seems like yesterday we were in the @ctkwbb van with Mr. C, aka U-turn Vinny 🤣🤣. Good luck in your next dance competition, @jboota 🙌🏾 #sisterhood #hoopsister #ctkroyals #friends

Cairo wanted to be outside, but soccer was moved inside due to the weather. He still had so much fun learning some new skills. Today he asked for a shirt ( jersey) with a number like his friend Enzo 🤣🤷🏽‍♀️ #youthsports #soccer #toddler #toddlerlife #mysonshine
Happy Pride! I’m thankful for my family and chosen family for all the love and support over the years. 🫶🏾 #lgbtq #loveislove #lovewins #love #pride #pridemonth #nyc

My eyes keep filling up with tears as I think about my big sis Nikki. I can see her face and that beautiful smile that was infectious. This one hurts. I’m praying for her family and loved ones during this difficult time. Rest in peace, sis. 💔🙏🏾 #nikkimccray #lvfl #washingtonmystics #ladyvols #tennessee #wnba #cancersucks

This video of Nikki brought a smile to my face. I hear her saying, “ Mique, why you do me like that? I’m going to get you back” 🤣. @coachpagina you see the moves. 📹: 1999 USA National team training. #nikkimccray #lvfl #washingtonmystics #ladyvols #tennessee #wnba #cancersucks

Happy 40th birthday to my wife, and a shout-out to the THINGS I’d rather do with her than with anyone else:⁣
Laugh, Play, Work, Dream,⁣
Stay Young, Grow Old⁣
Do Anything,⁣
Do Nothing. I love you ❤️
#40thbirthday #happybirthday #birthday #40andfabulous

Nikki always had a big smile and a great sense of humor. Yesterday was an amazing celebration of her life. You friend will always have a special place in my heart.❤️ #nikkimccraypenson #hoopsisters #ladyvols #tennessee #washingtonmystics #cancersucks

The kids enjoyed themselves at the @brownmillcompany anniversary block party. There were lots of activities for the kids and some dope vendors. After that we headed to Jersey City to watch lil Harold play in the @hoopsvilleproam and his team got the W. #familytime #family #summer #newjersey #brownmillcompany #hoops #vibes
I had a great time celebrating my cousin's 35th birthday. Love you, my fellow Leo @m_lp12. It's always fun linking up with family and friends. #sneakerball #birthday #leo #happybirthday #family

Yesterday, we celebrated me. Year 46! I’m so thankful to my God. 🙏🏾. ⁣
⁣
Thank you to everyone who reached out and wished me a happy birthday. I also appreciate those who popped up on me for dinner. ❤️⁣
⁣
I love African cuisine but have not been to Swahili village @swahilivillagenewarknj . The food and service were top-notch. Them lamb chops 😋🙌🏾. Thanks to my lovely wife for making the reservation and my sweet babies for the entertainment 🤣. #happybirthday ⁣#46yearsold #46 #livelaughlove #family #happy #blackgirlmagic

My babies are growing up too fast😩. We had so much fun at the volleyball match. They weren’t ready to go home and wanted to hang with @kassalaholdsclaw and Winny 🤷🏽‍♀️🤣🤣 #family #siblings #nyc #saturday #volleyball

My three year old son was doing the floss ( dance)yesterday. When I attempted to do it, he laughed and said I couldn’t dance 🤣. The nerve of him!! All I could do was laugh and think about the day the @washmystics Mayhem taught me a few moves. This video had me crying 😭. First of all, @coachpagina was throwing so much shade; secondly, my geriatric #griddy was painful to watch. 😂. Yes, I may have two left feet, but I’ll never stop dancing or trying to 🤷🏽‍♀️ #mysticmayhem #washingtonmystics #wnba #dance #happiness #laughteristhebestmedicine #laughter
Saturday mornings are always busy in our house. #family #familytime #pawpatrol #swimming #fitnessafter45 #love
My babies were lit this morning. 🤦🏾‍♀️. I was finally able to get them out of the house, and we met up with  @erinfahy for brunch. #sundayfunday #brunch #family #siblings

Hi everyone! Today is a special day. It’s my first baby's 30th birthday, so help me wish my little cousin @kassalaholdsclaw a Happy birthday 🎉. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
I’m so proud of the woman you are;  it’s been a joy watching you evolve and grow. Thank you for loving my babies; they love their Sala so much. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
A wise person once said, “We’re not here for a long time, so let’s make it a good time.” Never toast with an empty glass, always dance like no one’s watching” Stay safe and have fun ❤️⁣⁣
#family #cousins #happybirthday #30thbirthday

I’m saddened to hear of the passing of First Lady Rosalynn Carter. In 2015, she hosted a private dinner for my friends and me at the Carter Center before screening “Mind Game.” She shared some amazing stories about her journey, and I’m forever grateful for her and President Carter. She was a driving force in the field of mental health through her public service career. I  truly appreciate all the wisdom. RIP ❤️ #rosalynncarter #cartercenter #mentalhealthawareness #mentalhealth #firstlady

I’m so thankful I had the opportunity for my first babies, my first cousins  Thurman & Kassala, to spend time with my kids. This moment means so much to me. Of course, my wife and cousin Matty had to get in on all this love. ❤️ #family #familytime #happyholidays

Everyone help me wish my girl @la.ki.a a Happy birthday. Sorry, I'm not there to celebrate with you. I love how you keep growing and glowing. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
My bestie learned how to ride a bike this summer in Montreal, Canada. We were so excited for her. Here’s to more life 🥂❤️❤️ #montreal #canada #bestfriends #bestie #happybirthday

Happy birthday to our son Cairo who turned 4 on 12/14. I love you so much. You're such a smart, kind, and creative boy. I'm thankful for our family and village that continues to pour into his life. #happybirthday #4yearsold #sonshine #family #celebration
Happy Holidays! We wish you all the best this holiday season ❤️ #holidayseason #holiday #happynewyear
